text MeteorFalls_StevensCave_EventScript_Defeated {
    format("STEVEN: Oh, wow, {PLAYER}{KUN}. I'm amazed you knew where to find me.\p Do you, uh…maybe think of me as just a rock maniac?\p No, that can't be right.\p We battled alongside each other at the SOOTOPOLIS SPACE CENTER.\p You should have a very good idea about how good I am.\p Okay, {PLAYER}{KUN}, if you're going to mount a serious challenge, expect the worst!$ You… I had no idea you'd become so strong…$ STEVEN: Come to think of it, ever since our paths first crossed in GRANITE\l CAVE in DEWFORD, I had this feeling.\p I thought that you would eventually become the CHAMPION.\p My predictions usually come true.\p And where will you go from here?\p … … … … … … … … … … … …\p Fufufu, even I couldn't tell you that.")
}

